        <meta charset="utf-8">
    </head>
    <body>
        <h1>Whispers of the Wind</h1>
        <p>
            The wind speaks softly through the trees,<br>
            Carrying secrets on a gentle breeze.<br>
            It whispers tales from far away,<br>
            Of distant lands and skies of gray.<br><br>

            With every gust, it tells a song,<br>
            A melody that's sweet and strong.<br>
            The wind, a voice without a name,<br>
            Forever wild, yet never tame.
        </p>
    </body>
</html>


