<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <head>
        <meta charset="utf-8">
        <title>Challenge: Colorful creature</title>
    </head>
    <body>
        
        <h1>The coolest creature</h1>
        
        <!-- Adding an image of a peacock -->
        <img src="https://example.com/peacock.jpg" alt="A colorful peacock with vibrant feathers" width="600" height="400">
        
        <p>The <em>peacock</em> is awesome because <strong>it has some of the most vibrant and beautiful feathers in the animal kingdom</strong>. These feathers are used in courtship displays, where the male fans them out to attract a mate. The peacock's bright, iridescent tail feathers can have shades of blue, green, and gold, making it a truly magnificent creature.</p>
        
    </body>
</html>



